snippet.title: Weapon of Choice Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Weapon of Choice is a high-energy, side-scrolling action game with tons of unique weapons and playable characters used to fight a myriad of amazing monsters. 

Weapon of Choice is now available on your Xbox 360 for digital download in the Indie Games section.

Check out http://www.mommysbest.blogspot.com for new developments.
